{"tid":1172691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"德意志銀行研究部《2019全球物價報告》總體生活質素排名：日本14/新加坡23/韓國29/香港44","createTime":"2019-05-26T15:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T06:19:22.000Z","uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ed9eefe8ea497269ba1df628fa6bc17ec783117c","tid":1172691,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:08:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dbresearch.com/PROD/RPS_EN-PROD/PROD0000000000494405.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dbresearch.com%2FPROD%2FRPS_EN-PROD%2FPROD0000000000494405.pdf&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BRPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=e398933c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dbresearch.com/PROD/RPS_EN-PROD/PROD0000000000494405.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nkXzYix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnkXzYix.jpg&h=174c3d51&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n------------------------<br />\n<br />\nQuality-of-Life Indices (ranks) 生活質素排名<br />\n1,瑞士<br />\n2,紐西蘭<br />\n3,丹麥<br />\n...<br />\n14,日本 (亞洲國家第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n...<br />\n23,新加坡<br />\n29,韓國<br />\n...<br />\n44,香港<br />\n<br />\n------------------------<br />\n<br />\nMonthly Salary (Net of Taxes)<br />\n11,新加坡<br />\n13,日本 (最低工資70港元，東京)<br />\n...<br />\n27,香港 (最低工資37.5港元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n28,韓國 (最低工資58港元)<br />\n<br />\n------------------------<br />\n<br />\nMonthly Rent for Mid-Range 2 Bedroom Apartment<br />\n1,香港 (大勝!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n...<br />\n10,日本<br />\n11,新加坡<br />\n...<br />\n23,韓國<br />\n<br />\n------------------------<br />\n連登日韓專家評論：<br />\n你地踩港撚知唔知...日韓工作壓力好大，一定要OT，日日俾上司鬧<br />\n人地自殺率高，壓力好大，相反香港社會好輕鬆，無人會自殺<br />\n人工高無用，因為要扣稅，而且物價更貴，食一餐飯100蚊港幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GTxwf6K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGTxwf6K.png&h=c51e1fbe&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連登新加坡專家評論：<br />\n你地踩港撚知唔知...新加坡人都係坡豬，唔鬧得政府，無自由，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我寧願住香港訓係龍床上面鬧政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新加坡地鐵會炒車好垃圾，港鐵秒殺新加坡地鐵，MTR萬歲，自豪呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4d65d5f3784c2082477d60d7bce45a37ce4f2e","tid":1172691,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbbb49d029aaaf6f9654549a4d4fe754a7179ed9","tid":1172691,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed9eefe8ea497269ba1df628fa6bc17ec783117c","tid":1172691,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:08:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dbresearch.com/PROD/RPS_EN-PROD/PROD0000000000494405.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dbresearch.com%2FPROD%2FRPS_EN-PROD%2FPROD0000000000494405.pdf&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BRPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=e398933c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dbresearch.com/PROD/RPS_EN-PROD/PROD0000000000494405.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nkXzYix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnkXzYix.jpg&h=174c3d51&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n------------------------<br />\n<br />\nQuality-of-Life Indices (ranks) 生活質素排名<br />\n1,瑞士<br />\n2,紐西蘭<br />\n3,丹麥<br />\n...<br />\n14,日本 (亞洲國家第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n...<br />\n23,新加坡<br />\n29,韓國<br />\n...<br />\n44,香港<br />\n<br />\n------------------------<br />\n<br />\nMonthly Salary (Net of Taxes)<br />\n11,新加坡<br />\n13,日本 (最低工資70港元，東京)<br />\n...<br />\n27,香港 (最低工資37.5港